ResourceHeader.ResourceName: Radio JOVE HNRAO LWA+FSX2 Spectrograph 15-30 MHz Dynamic Spectrograms
ResourceHeader.Description:
Dynamic Spectrogram plots from output of the HNRAO
   LWA-type 4 phase crossed dipoles square array and FSX2 Spectrograph operating from 15-30 MHz. The plots
   are generated using the Radio-Sky Spectrograph software. The Display Cadence will
   vary but 8 hours is a reasonable maximum value for the timespan of
   a single file. Time is presented in Universal Time (UT).
